 ta-path-to-node="13"><strong data-path-to-node="13" data-index-in-node="0
 ">Biography: Ambassador &amp\; Professor Lee Feinstein</strong></h3><p da
 ta-path-to-node="14">  Ambassador Lee Feinstein is a Senior Managing Dire
 ctor and the President of McLarty Associates. He previously served as the
  U.S. Ambassador to the Republic of Poland and held senior positions at t
 he Department of State\, including Principal Deputy Director and a Member
  of the Policy Planning Staff. He was the Founding Dean of the Hamilton L
 ugar School of Global and International Studies at Indiana University fro
 m 2014 to 2022. Ambassador Feinstein is a member of the Council on Foreig
 n Relations and the American Academy of Diplomacy\, and holds a JD from G
 eorgetown University Law Center.</p><p data-path-to-node="14">  &#160\;</
 p><p data-path-to-node="14"><em><strong>Can't make the full hour? No prob
